                              PREAMBLE
================================================================================

This license governs the use of the Simjot Poetry Engine ("the Engine"), which includes
all source code, algorithms, data structures, and specifications contained within
the `main.core.poetry` package and its subpackages.

The Engine implements proprietary natural language processing and poetry analysis
technology exclusively designed for use within the Simjot journaling application.
This license permits inspection and study of the source code while prohibiting
incorporation into other projects.

