1. DEFINITIONS

   1.1 "Engine" refers to the Simjot Poetry Engine, including but not limited to:
       - PoetryAnalyzer.java and all analysis implementations
       - SyllableCounter.java and phonetic analysis classes
       - RhymeEngine.java and rhyme detection algorithms
       - MeterAnalyzer.java and poetic meter analysis
       - PoeticForm.java and form recognition classes
       - Any documentation, comments, or specifications within these files
       - The proprietary poetry analysis algorithms and data structures

   1.2 "Simjot Application" refers to the Simjot journaling software and any
       official derivatives, updates, or versions thereof.

   1.3 "Inspection" refers to reading, studying, and analyzing the source code
       for educational, research, or auditing purposes.

   1.4 "Use" refers to compiling, executing, integrating, or incorporating the
       Engine or any portion thereof into any software system.

